data.description: Stunning home with amazing layout will have you boasting with excitement that this home is ready for new owners. With a full price offer, Seller will pay $15,000 closing cost, WOW! Tax rate at 1.331% no city taxes, even better. You will fall in love with this gorgeous home and community. Ready for the holidays with a fireplace you can see from dining rooms, living room and the kitchen. Butlers pantry with sink, refrigerator, granite counter tops, built in wine rack, decorative lighting, nothing was missed on this custom home.Separate entry to 2nd floor. Love outdoor living, you'll love the large sun room and the outside custom fireplace, built in grill and the low maintenance outdoor space. 3 bedrooms 1st floor,2 flex spaces and bedroom up. 3 car garage with lift to easily move furniture upstairs with ease. Pecan Plantation, is a must see to believe. Golf, grocery, doctors, club house, pools,tennis, air strip, guarded entry, fishing, lake, stables, marina, walking trails and much more.
